  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OTHER GAMES FROM OPALA PROJECT</h1><p><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1641565800\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1641565800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1641565800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/1cd9511cf1da82b1304dc1d7fef5cf24.avif?t=1641565800\" width=736 height=150 /></span><br><br>This is an original puzzle game inspired by basketball. With the ball, you need to move around the grids until you finish your movements limit, find the correct position to make shots and then finish your turn by scoring a basket!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Characters move according to their ability, but the goal is to use your movements to reach the basket;<br></li><li> 30 creative levels with increasing complexity;<br></li><li> A basketball game without basketball. This is an entirely new game concept for basketball lovers and newbies (you don't need to know basketball to play it);<br></li><li> Enjoy the beauty and dangers of Saturn and many cats;<br></li><li> Soundtracks originally composed.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/503aa6fc77344d66ad99e5b6b696e97f.avif?t=1641565800\" width=736 height=150 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/1cd9511cf1da82b1304dc1d7fef5cf24.avif?t=1641565800\" width=736 height=150 /></span><br><br>This is an original puzzle game inspired by basketball. With the ball, you need to move around the grids until you finish your movements limit, find the correct position to make shots and then finish your turn by scoring a basket!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Characters move according to their ability, but the goal is to use your movements to reach the basket;<br></li><li> 30 creative levels with increasing complexity;<br></li><li> A basketball game without basketball. This is an entirely new game concept for basketball lovers and newbies (you don't need to know basketball to play it);<br></li><li> Enjoy the beauty and dangers of Saturn and many cats;<br></li><li> Soundtracks originally composed.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575860/extras/503aa6fc77344d66ad99e5b6b696e97f.avif?t=1641565800\" width=736 height=150 /></span>",
